1
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:56,290
If I had known you were waiting at home,

2
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:59,160
I would have brought your little brother back too.

3
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:05,560
I thought the guy who got the passports, rescued Jessica,

4
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,920
and took down Zhang Defa

5
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,360
would either be as strong as Lu Bu

6
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:12,720
or as cunning as Sima Yi.

7
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,920
I didn't expect that after seeing you,

8
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:18,160
I'd think you're more like Li Wenming,

9
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,480
and you're even sick.

10
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,810
It's quite surprising.

11
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,040
Who is Li Wenming?

12
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,000
The security guard downstairs.

13
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,000
Thank you for the compliment.

14
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,920
You guys go out first.

15
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,530
Now that they've both left,

16
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,880
why don't you invite me to sit down

17
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,140
and we can talk slowly?

18
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,770
You've been here for over half an hour, right?

19
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,440
You've probably rummaged through my bed.

20
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,640
Do you still need me to invite you to sit?

21
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,880
Let's talk.

22
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:06,160
Then I'll get straight to the point.

23
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,640
Shao Yu,

24
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,800
from Tangzhou.

25
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:12,120
Admitted to Tangzhou Police Academy 18 years ago,

26
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:15,330
graduated with the best grades in the last ten years,

27
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,560
and directly joined the criminal investigation team.

28
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,800
Badge number 016933.

29
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,800
And you became the youngest captain

30
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:25,040
of the criminal investigation team in Tangzhou's history.

31
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,920
Four years ago, during a hostage rescue operation,

32
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,960
you recklessly shot and killed a suspect.

33
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,520
So you were disciplined

34
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,980
and dismissed from the police force.

35
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:38,610
After that, you started a small business.

36
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,960
But because of your wife's early death,

37
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:43,280
you had to raise your daughter alone.

38
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:46,880
However, you never stepped out of the shadow of taking off your uniform.

39
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:50,520
So, neither your subsequent career nor your life

40
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,210
has been particularly satisfactory.

41
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:56,240
And you haven't given enough care to your daughter's growth,

42
00:04:56,240 --> 00:05:00,000
resulting in a not very harmonious father-daughter relationship.

43
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:03,400
Actually, you've always felt guilty towards your daughter.

44
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,240
She became your weakness.

45
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,960
When others use her to threaten you,

46
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,760
you will do whatever it takes

47
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,490
and are willing to do anything.

48
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,050
You investigated thoroughly.

49
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,880
But since you investigated so much,

50
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,200
you should also know

51
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,000
that I am just a pawn.

52
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,480
So you shouldn't look for me.

53
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,540
You should look for the chess player.

54
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,080
Right.

55
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,200
Although you are just a pawn,

56
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,560
you did do some things after all.

57
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:32,010
You have to take some responsibility.

58
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,440
I can give you a chance.

59
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,400
Help me find that person,

60
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,800
and I'll let bygones be bygones.

61
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,680
Moreover...

62
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:45,159
We can also help you save your daughter.

63
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,860
My daughter is in their hands now.

64
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,680
I can't take that risk.

65
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,100
Don't be in such a hurry to refuse.

66
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:02,600
You don't know much about me and the people behind me yet.

67
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:06,000
We are absolutely capable of helping you save your daughter.

68
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,840
Of course, from another perspective,

69
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:11,460
we can also make you and your daughter

70
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,320
disappear forever.

71
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:27,180
Contact me when you've made up your mind.

72
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,159
That's fine.

73
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,360
We still have plenty of time.

74
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,760
If you change your mind,

75
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:44,880
you can find me.

76
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,200
Why are you here?

77
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,060
Let's find a place to talk.

78
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,200
I'm working right now.

79
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,600
Wait until I get off work.

80
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,840
What's wrong with you?

81
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,200
Where is my daughter?

82
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,680
Why did you hurt her?

83
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:54,000
I...

84
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,720
I don't know what you're talking about.

85
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,120
I know everything.

86
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,400
Stop pretending, okay?

87
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,600
Wait a minute.

88
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,860
I'll go change my clothes.

89
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:17,680
How did you know?

90
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,400
You said you never cook,

91
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,730
and only order takeout.

92
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,640
But you have a habit.

93
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:27,480
You tear off the personal information section on the receipt

94
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,480
very neatly.

95
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,920
Aunt Liu,

96
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:33,720
could you please clear the takeout from the table?

97
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,919
Earlier at Zi's house,

98
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:43,760
I saw that on her leftover takeout bags,

99
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:46,620
the personal info section was also neatly torn off.

100
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,090
Exactly the same as your habit.

101
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,760
I didn't pay much attention to it then,

102
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,040
but now I understand.

103
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,760
You must have been to Zi's house.

104
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,720
You guys are together.

105
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:06,360
And my CT report, you prepared it in advance, didn't you?

106
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:09,040
Before, I had abdominal discomfort,

107
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,300
so I went for a checkup.

108
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,840
But the day the report came out,

109
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,640
something happened to my daughter,

110
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,400
so I didn't get a chance to read it.

111
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:18,460
Today, I accidentally saw the report

112
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:22,100
that suspected a tumor in my abdomen.

113
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,720
But the strange thing is,

114
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:28,320
after you told me there was a foreign object in my abdomen,

115
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,800
all my discomfort

116
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,260
completely disappeared.

117
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,120
Today I got a CT scan,

118
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,440
and I found out

119
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:37,140
there is no foreign object in my abdomen.

120
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,720
To set up this bomb mechanism,

121
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:42,640
you conveniently removed my tumor.

122
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,340
You did it, didn't you?

123
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:49,880
You and Zi kidnapped my daughter

124
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:52,840
and used her to threaten me into doing your tasks.

125
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:56,200
You just cut open my belly

126
00:09:56,960 --> 00:10:00,160
and used the wound to make me believe there was a bomb.

127
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:04,260
I guess you put anti-inflammatory drugs in my abdomen,

128
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,360
wrapped in a dissolvable coating.

129
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,360
After a certain time,

130
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,280
the coating dissolved,

131
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,680
and I would feel pain

132
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,680
and believe there was a bomb.

133
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,880
Of course,

134
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:20,360
you probably thought it wasn't foolproof enough,

135
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,290
afraid I might get a CT scan myself.

136
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,320
So you figured out a way

137
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,520
to make that bullied boy

138
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,080
appear near your clinic.

139
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:32,360
I took him to you for treatment,

140
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:35,040
and coincidentally got a CT scan there.

141
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:38,320
Then you could use the prepared report

142
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:40,640
to completely solidify this story.

143
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:51,440
You kept following me on the pretext

144
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:54,160
of needing further checks for the foreign object.

145
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:56,420
Actually, it was just to spy on me, right?

146
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,680
If it was just to spy on you,

147
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,220
it wouldn't be this troublesome.

148
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,040
I was genuinely worried about you,

149
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,500
afraid you'd be in danger.

150
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:09,280
Put away your fake face, okay?

151
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:12,160
My purpose for finding you today is simple.

152
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,360
Tell me where my daughter is.

153
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:15,820
Otherwise,

154
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,010
I don't know what I might do.

155
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,920
I really don't know where she is.

156
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:28,680
I was forced to do all this.

157
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:31,700
What did they use to force you?

158
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:35,120
I can't say.

159
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,600
But I will try my best to help you

160
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,880
rescue your daughter.

161
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,010
How will you help me?

162
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,520
My daughter's pinky

163
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,200
was cut off.

164
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,600
What?

165
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:59,120
I didn't expect things to go this far.

166
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:01,960
I thought they just wanted to scare you.

167
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,800
I don't believe what you say.

168
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,280
I only believe what I see.

169
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,780
Give me your phone.

170
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,240
I'm really not lying.

171
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:32,130
They all contacted me directly using this phone.

172
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:36,160
Whether you're lying or not,

173
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,410
and whether you were forced or not,

174
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,860
what I want to tell you now is this:

175
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:43,280
If my daughter gets hurt again,

176
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,560
even just a little bit,

177
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,720
all of you

178
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:52,040
will pay the price.

179
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,280
Come in.

180
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:01,680
Good memory.

181
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:04,810
You memorized my number with just one glance.

182
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:08,160
Contact me when you've decided.

183
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,080
My home is not safe right now.

184
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:18,360
They probably installed cameras.

185
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,800
They have my daughter right now.

186
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,200
I can't take that risk.

187
00:14:23,040 --> 00:14:25,200
So you had to reject me back then.

188
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:28,600
I have no hostility towards you.

189
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:30,240
They are my real enemies.

190
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:34,800
I'll cooperate with you.

191
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,240
Help me save my daughter.

192
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:37,960
No problem.

193
00:14:38,640 --> 00:14:40,520
After all, you proved your loyalty

194
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:42,520
by exposing the female doctor to us.

195
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,880
I knew you would follow me.

196
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:46,740
But she's just a minor character.

197
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:49,240
You'd better not touch her yet,

198
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:49,920
because

199
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:52,170
she might be useful to me later.

200
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:56,560
I finally understand why they chose you.

201
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,850
Let's get down to business.

202
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,810
You said you guys are powerful.

203
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:13,560
So what can you offer me?

204
00:15:15,280 --> 00:15:17,800
We can provide any resources you want.

205
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,400
And,

206
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,680
if I'm not mistaken,

207
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,920
your next mission

208
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,800
is to get a USB drive.

209
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,200
A new mission is here.

210
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:40,480
Get a USB drive for me.
